a) suspend the provision of services approved, subsidized, or organized by the French community;
b) identify the methods by which activities can be carried out to reduce social contacts;
c) restrict or limit access to buildings;
d)  adopt the requirements for attendance, assessment, and authorization of classes to the suspension of courses and learning activities;
